game.name: Instagirls Halloween Dress Up
game.description:
The darkest night of the year is just around and all people of the city are ready to make arrangements to make this year Halloween celebration something special! These Instagirls are no different from them and looking forward to shop for the new Halloween costume. Would you guide them to enjoy a hassle-free shopping spree? Join Instagirls Halloween Dress Up and be prepared to choose a perfect Halloween outfit and show it off on their instagram profile! Many more excitements and achievements are there to explore to get more coins. 

Start this brand new girls game by picking your girl and taking her for shopping! Remember you have a particular budget to spend on your purchasing of multiple products. Grab the suit first and then go with a strapless green fairy outfit along with a black color dress with spider webs! Choose a mummy suit, a glittery flapper dress with fringes or a Little Riding Hood dress! Try to mix and match as many beautiful tops and bottoms as you can to prepare an awesome Harley Quinn, a skeleton or an Egyptian Queen in this HTML5 dressing game! 

Purchase some cool accessories like a pair of matching shoes, a nurse hat, a black lace face mask, a pair of devil horns, a veil or a chic hairstyle! Dress your girls with the best new outfits, took their pictures and post them on their instagram accounts! Wait for a moment how many likes they are able to score shortly! You would have 7 unique models select from and 15 outfit goals to complete. Enjoy more funny free Halloween games on atmegame.com and have a blast for free with your friends, no download required!
